casebody.head_matter:
Robert A. RUCHO, et al., applicants,
v.
COMMON CAUSE, et al.
No. 17A745.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 6, 2018.
The motion of appellees to construe the application for stay as a jurisdictional statement and for an expedited briefing and oral argument schedule is denied.
Justice GINSBURG and Justice SOTOMAYOR would grant the motion.
